tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE employee_satisfaction_survey (
    survey_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    employee_id INT,
    satisfaction_score INT,
    feedback TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE employee_survey (employee_id INT, satisfaction_score INT, department VARCHAR(50), manager_name VARCHAR(50));
CREATE TABLE survey_questions (question_id INT, question_text TEXT);

CREATE TABLE employee_survey_data (
  employee_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  satisfaction_score INT,
  department VARCHAR,
  date_of_survey DATE
)

CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
  response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  question_id INT,
 employee_id INT,
 response_text TEXT,
 survey_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE survey_questions (
  question_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  question_text TEXT,
 question_category VARCHAR
)
CREATE TABLE Employee ( employee_id INT PRIMARY KEY, employee_name STRING, department STRING, satisfaction_score INT )
CREATE TABLE Department ( department_id INT PRIMARY KEY, department_name STRING )
CREATE TABLE SurveyResponse ( response_id INT PRIMARY KEY, employee_id INT, survey_date DATE, satisfaction_rating INT, feedback STRING )
CREATE TABLE FeedbackAnalysis ( analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY, analysis_date DATE, analysis_description STRING )
